Documentation for Stability of Chaotic maps

This project is a collection of tools to plot logistic maps and its iterations.

See: Description

Package Description
crypto  
main  
servlet  
This project is a collection of tools to plot logistic maps and its iterations. It also serves to plot Filled Julia Sets or Fractals.
This project also contains a module which is an implementation of the paper Image Encryption Using Logistic Maps. Please Go through the paper once to understand the project code.
You might want to read README.md to know how to setup the project and all the dependencies.
